Text: Awesome torrent, I wanted copies of those specials. I think you are missing one broadcast program; I didn't see The Doctor, the Widow and the Wardrobe in there anywhere. Thanks for the upload though, JBX32!
You should watch the episodes in this order: https://docs.google.com/spreadsheet/ccc?key=0AoIGnN0sVZGudHlPRkwxbE1jc3lvbmlLNE85MFBkWEE#gid=0
